{"tid":1229541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非勇武並存。今日要和平，只限今日！","createTime":"2019-06-16T03:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T05:11:23.000Z","uid":33565,"like":121,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3296429c963864cafb9fff3dd5f25b47221510bf","tid":1229541,"uid":33565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:22:12.000Z","msg":"今日616，希望大家和平進行，因為今日一齊遊行既同伴，未必預計到會有一班人沖，到時效果一定係負平多，大家可以參考返6月9同 6月12 兩次行動，點解大家都支持，點解可以和理非同勇武合作到，就係因為互不侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家係一個主張和理非表達既活動到勇武表達，必定會引起分化，政府大條道理指責，再加埋紅底傳媒鋪天蓋地既宣傳，今日勇武既人一定會輸，成本太大。<br />\n要勇武既留返起一日開張明義要衝擊既日子，大家都支持，但唔會係今次遊行，唔好因為憤怒同沮喪而衝擊，勇武既行動一定要出師有名，先可以引起社會支持，而6月12 就係一個好例子。<br />\n<br />\n經過琴晚既事，見到好多戰友話今日就要流血革命（可以參考返每個因烈士而開既post），我相信每一位今日出席既同伴都會明白，香港政府，政權，警犬真係痴撚線，但唔好因為咁而強逼其他人一齊陪你勇武，如果唔係就指責批評，至少今日唔應該係。<br />\n<br />\n小弟6月9同6月12 都發夢出席，亦都走在前線，我係絕對支持革命需要留血，但絕不同意係今日反生，我而家已經出左門，見到街頭好多黑色衫既一家大細，如果係呢班平時沉默既人面前發生衝突，後果絕對係不敢想像，如果有人因係咁而離隊，絕對係反送中戰友既損失。<br />\n<br />\n要勇武升級，一定要一鼓作氣，唔好以不斷既零星衝突，街頭抗爭為表達方法，一係就擇日full gear再出發，而呢段時間其間，必需靠大家文宣工作做好，要引發一次大規模，甚至比612 更大既活動。 <br />\n<br />\n最後呼籲多次，今日係和平遊行，唔好衝唔好分化，勇武和理非各自做事，因為一撈埋實仆街。香港加油，必須要有成果以際英靈。<br />\n<br />\nRIP"},{"pid":"6089469ab404c978d0877b18a86d8b3667919dc7","tid":1229541,"uid":33565,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:24:58.000Z","msg":"請以正負分風向，如果我錯，我一定陪大家衝，烈士既血唔會白流，立此為證"},{"pid":"c2041de91a7df9fc2b37ce0b505d875cec6cb327","tid":1229541,"uid":132128,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:25:56.000Z","msg":"又唱今天我？"},{"pid":"ea4d3b05729ec3a6576307d51da0e52f4978c879","tid":1229541,"uid":33565,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c2041de91a7df9fc2b37ce0b505d875cec6cb327","tid":1229541,"uid":132128,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:25:56.000Z","msg":"又唱今天我？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:26:46.000Z","msg":"邊一句令你覺得我意思係咁？ 6月9有冇人唱？"},{"pid":"b38aedfc3a7f9db9a3f63967dbd633f5e533baf9","tid":1229541,"uid":198236,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:27:22.000Z","msg":"同埋今日可能多小朋友同公公婆婆，安全啲好"},{"pid":"f3f8eaefa15f6d2b52be884b6dd58526c602b8b7","tid":1229541,"uid":191701,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:27:30.000Z","msg":"agger 不可以再比藉口政府搞搞震"},{"pid":"0be8de62e0efff14f4e62986cac138d4d1f28776","tid":1229541,"uid":33565,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c2041de91a7df9fc2b37ce0b505d875cec6cb327","tid":1229541,"uid":132128,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:25:56.000Z","msg":"又唱今天我？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:28:13.000Z","msg":"我一直都係話，如果兩邊派系，和理非勇武一齊既活動，應該要和平表達，至少今日係，將來唔敢講，但只限今日"},{"pid":"599547b4f3e5af574664632a2eccc45ce570ce36","tid":1229541,"uid":44243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c2041de91a7df9fc2b37ce0b505d875cec6cb327","tid":1229541,"uid":132128,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:25:56.000Z","msg":"又唱今天我？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:28:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"7ea99ac0c7f9694239b3ad97ad6d5124b6ba8735","tid":1229541,"uid":38535,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:29:00.000Z","msg":"衝去邊先得架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n愛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7e7514e15be73ba2388547ea61b398e1f4ecc6","tid":1229541,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:29:27.000Z","msg":"入左夜就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7287bbaa307296c2084516ff40802df10a198974","tid":1229541,"uid":33565,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:29:53.000Z","msg":"勇武都要有凝聚力，唔係話突然衝就衝。<br />\n再打個比喻，如果講到明今個星期幾號，要包圍邊度邊度，我一撚定支持，亦不計代價"},{"pid":"4f1dfb0ec85cd48c28ad7a34e1bf3932eb47f9c9","tid":1229541,"uid":78399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:30:50.000Z","msg":"不嬲要共存<br />\n事實上係得任何一邊都唔得<br />\n6.12 係基於6.9政府既唔回應"},{"pid":"9bc2512fd985a2315e1e50cad9443d9574012ed4","tid":1229541,"uid":33565,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:31:39.000Z","msg":"今日衝，一撚定會趕走班和理非，沖出反割蔗。<br />\n我係好撚同意要衝要勇武，但我由頭到尾都係講，不是今天"},{"pid":"013ccf5027964ff3314cd80ab6fb149aa5eb68c9","tid":1229541,"uid":33875,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"唔係唔可以衝，但唔係今日衝<br />\n我絕對相信前線抗爭者識得自行判斷，今日黑衫白花默行送別逝去義士<br />\n他朝再為佢報仇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81789316185bc91bb7ea115569d246fa607e5f7e","tid":1229541,"uid":33565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:33:45.000Z","msg":"今日衝既人，唔係鬼，只係我認為今日衝，會得不償失，我都係勇武，不過我唔建議今日衝，要衝擇日再戰"},{"pid":"818b939e97faac1704c8d539537add35daccc8d2","tid":1229541,"uid":118827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:34:11.000Z","msg":"唔好比武力 趕走小朋友 顧家既父母 老人家 廢老"},{"pid":"9b18adef2ed5df8ceb4f82ed21a9f3469603b453","tid":1229541,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb8cab0c8bd3627f1d4c63a171ba066ff2bc7ce","tid":1229541,"uid":33565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要追究政府班仆街同打手"},{"pid":"c08a07beaf855ad705ebf20bcbd3365d454c2f79","tid":1229541,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:37:06.000Z","msg":"今日純粹出黎曬馬證明示威者係唔接受暫緩<br />\n無必要衝，除非佢突擊攞返出黎二讀"},{"pid":"f1f336038da3b4185649df7c89a3b5507239db43","tid":1229541,"uid":78399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"db7e7514e15be73ba2388547ea61b398e1f4ecc6","tid":1229541,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:29:27.000Z","msg":"入左夜就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:37:22.000Z","msg":"入夜 記者唔會影到相幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開槍都睇唔到 6.12咁大回嚮就係因為 日光日白<br />\n警察清清楚楚開左槍 你睇下邊有一次入夜係成功既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6.17民陣應該要繼續集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f19295542c0752a6afc93e71dc3e3e18afcc42a","tid":1229541,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7ce4e31811c42de0624db6dd723057ee4d7f3a","tid":1229541,"uid":33565,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c08a07beaf855ad705ebf20bcbd3365d454c2f79","tid":1229541,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:37:06.000Z","msg":"今日純粹出黎曬馬證明示威者係唔接受暫緩<br />\n無必要衝，除非佢突擊攞返出黎二讀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:40:16.000Z","msg":"仲要比國際睇到香港人既意志同決心，所以今日要做得好好睇睇，今日政府唔發聲唔徹回。<br />\n<br />\n下次勇武更加出師有名，因為大家都慢慢同意，和平無用，但如果今天就即刻兩派混埋一齊做，逼人割蔗，代價太大。而家每一步都要小心行，我地既敵人、呢個政府絕對會抽住你一個失誤無限放大"},{"pid":"36a07e91ec68154bed603bce7fe73516bf657900","tid":1229541,"uid":33565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:42:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4996ba8cdf6fec25a6a7c08205ac24136adc83ec","tid":1229541,"uid":33565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:46: